00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:02.670
This really is, I know, important
in all your lives and a cause.

00:03:02.670 --> 00:03:04.570
You know, literacy
certainly is a cause.

00:03:04.570 --> 00:03:07.730
So, let me say that before
