of the new rapid-acting
antidepressants like ketamine,

00:34:07.230 --> 00:34:10.460
it seem to have activity
after a single administration.

00:34:10.460 --> 00:34:11.760
&gt;&gt; Dr. Peter Kramer: Right.

00:34:11.760 --> 00:34:14.680
&gt;&gt; And even some reports that
they block suicidal ideation.

00:34:14.680 --> 00:34:15.980
&gt;&gt; Dr. Peter Kramer: Right.

00:34:15.980 --> 00:34:20.080
So, there's a lot of interest in a
drug that was used as an anesthetic

00:34:20.080 --> 00:34:24.050
and misused as a party drug
called ketamine which is given

00:34:24.050 --> 00:34:26.860
through injections into the muscle

00:34:26.860 --> 00:34:30.710
or intravenously dripped
into the veins.

00:34:30.710 --> 00:34:39.040 position:56%
And it was first used in people with
very severe hospitalized patients

00:34:39.040 --> 00:34:40.340
with very severe depression.

00:34:40.340 --> 00:34:42.820 position:56%
And some of them got better rapidly.

00:34:42.820 --> 00:34:45.480
And drug companies are interested
