00:36:32.140 --> 00:36:35.140
that is you start calling your
friends again, you start putting

00:36:35.140 --> 00:36:39.180
in more effort at work, people will
reward that so that there's sort

00:36:39.180 --> 00:36:44.650
of a virtuous dialectic between
the chemical action and the social

00:36:44.650 --> 00:36:46.880
and psychological action
of these medicines.

00:36:46.880 --> 00:36:50.530
But we do get some
effect very early.

00:36:50.530 --> 00:36:52.140
&gt;&gt; Leonard Bernstein: I
think we have someone here.

00:36:52.140 --> 00:36:54.780
&gt;&gt; Yeah. Could you
